## Introduction:

Library Carpentry introduces you to the fundamentals of computing and provides you with a platform for further self-directed learning. It is here to help you automate repetitive, boring, error-prone tasks; create, maintain and analyze sustainable and reusable data; work effectively with IT and systems colleagues;better understand the use of software in research.


## Topics:

* Tidy Data
* Working with Data
* UNIX Shell
* OpenRefine


## Dates

* August 14 - September 04 
* Every Friday
* 12:00 pm - 03:00 pm EDT


## Location

* Zoom


